front.title: •Gailid
front.gametext: Deploys free to same site as Mosep. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. While at Audience Chamber, adds 1 to your Force drains at Jabba's Palace sites.
front.lore: Mosep's assistant. Accountant. Tax collector. Enjoys tending to Jabba's skiffs with Barada.

canceledBy: Game text canceled by Freon Drevan if at same or adjacent site
